Get S&P+ historical rating data

cfb_ratings_sp.Rd

At least one of year or team must be specified for the function to run

cfb_ratings_sp(year = NULL, team = NULL)

Arguments

year

(Integer optional): Year, 4 digit format (YYYY)
team

(String optional): D-I Team

Source

https://api.collegefootballdata.com/ratings/sp

Value

A data frame with 26 variables:

year

integer.

team

character.
